=== sw-cor24-rpg-ii Minimal RPG-II Demo ===
Program:
H  control header
F  input file INFIL
I  field A0110  (10-char input slice)
C  MOVE A0110 -> calc work field
O  DETAIL output (10 chars)

Current boundary:
- Real today: build path, external tiny source-deck loading, fixed H/F/I/C/O
  source parsing, one extracted field, one MOVE-style calc stage, one
  output-line format stage, live runtime-produced CLI demo surface.
- Placeholder today: only a tiny narrow subset varies; there is still no
  general RPG parser, no variable C-spec execution, no general O-spec
  formatting, and no arbitrary user-supplied RPG program execution yet.

Current runtime-produced output:
RECORD 01A
RECORD 02B
RECORD 03C



